To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private HangingMan _hangingman;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_hangingman = HangingMan(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_hangingman.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "hangingman", _hangingman.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.hangingman = self.HangingMan(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.hangingman.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "hangingman", self.hangingman.Current.Value)
